"          <font class=\"text-o-color-1\">Website App </font>\n"
"        </strong>and <strong>\n"
"          <font class=\"text-o-color-1\">CRM App</font>\n"
"        </strong>!"
msgstr ""
"Cree su sitio web gratuito y obtenga leads de forma pasiva con <strong>\n"
"          <font class=\"text-o-color-1\">la aplicación Sitio web </font>\n"
"        </strong>y <strong>\n"
"          <font class=\"text-o-color-1\">la aplicación CRM</font>\n"
"        </strong>"

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Some plan, others produce... Open the <strong>Shop Floor App</strong> to "
"manufacture\n"
"      products."
msgstr ""
"Algunos planifican, otros producen... Abra la <strong>aplicación Taller</"
"strong> para fabricar\n"
"      los productos."

#. module: food_distribution
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:food_distribution.welcome_article_body
msgid "Some rules are defined to easily resupply ingredients and containers."
msgstr ""
